{"tid":2260242,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個最欣賞嘅台灣藝人","createTime":"2020-10-27T12:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T05:24:43.000Z","uid":195944,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3b1bb6e8d63e17883469bc14ff7bbc44fb7a2a53","tid":2260242,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:26:23.000Z","msg":"我先 kid<br />\n<br />\n從以前一個做野講野唔經大腦慢慢成長變成一個愛錫身邊人受人歡迎嘅野人<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢私生活都唔太檢點 當兵又搞出大頭佛 但起碼無大頭症 好敬業 不忘本<br />\n<br />\n野人七號部落見到佢廣交朋友 都係咁貪玩但多咗一份謙虛<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCESIRUtUaGfqWCgljB1EB2A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCESIRUtUaGfqWCgljB1EB2A&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=397a05ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCESIRUtUaGfqWCgljB1EB2A</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知佢有無奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但希望佢繼續扎根台灣 宣傳台灣美好一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家又有無中意嘅台灣藝人呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f998026c195368323271790756d79d63a8f7fb37","tid":2260242,"uid":63651,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:27:00.000Z","msg":"焦安溥（張懸）<br />\n不解釋"},{"pid":"4ad32311bc9d74a3b6783d3a836402fc535b3c72","tid":2260242,"uid":134012,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:27:46.000Z","msg":"台哥"},{"pid":"1105dc71d50d1c36bc81372d1d456ab404a2477b","tid":2260242,"uid":375893,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:28:29.000Z","msg":"小鬼<br />\n不解釋"},{"pid":"7b3bc91cbf568931ca457bc0691a44ea80ec3f35","tid":2260242,"uid":20262,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"雞排妹"},{"pid":"d773a255278d17e338a12aa07ad88dd9a048e8ff","tid":2260242,"uid":117903,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:29:06.000Z","msg":"黃鴻